708115f-a.title: Manhattan: 3rd Avenue - 66th Street
708115f-a.text:
Third Avenue, west side, north from 66th to o7th Streets. The corner
house (Stein's Shoe Store) is No. 1130 Third Avenue. The new
building on 66th Street, just showing at the left, was built
in 1916.
About 1920.
Edwin Levick, Photographer.
Cift of E. M. Jenks.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
